Class AnnotatingPass

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CompileTimePass, Serializable, Function<DAG<IRVertex,IREdge>,DAG<IRVertex,IREdge>>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DataSkewEdgeDataStorePass, DataSkewEdgeMetricCollectionPass, DataSkewEdgePartitionerPass, DataSkewVertexPass, DefaultEdgeUsedDataHandlingPass, DefaultParallelismPass, DefaultStagePartitioningPass, DisaggregationEdgeDataStorePass, PadoEdgeDataFlowModelPass, PadoEdgeDataStorePass, PadoVertexExecutorPlacementPass, ReviseInterStageEdgeDataStorePass, SailfishEdgeDataFlowModelPass, SailfishEdgeDataStorePass, SailfishEdgeUsedDataHandlingPass, ScheduleGroupPass, ShuffleEdgePushPass

    public abstract class AnnotatingPass
extends Object
implements CompileTimePass
    A compile-time pass that annotates the IR DAG with execution properties. It is ensured by the compiler that the shape of the IR DAG itself is not modified by an AnnotatingPass.
